    PrepareAnswer --> GenerateResponse[Create Natural Language Response<br/>Using Retrieved Information]
    
    GenerateResponse --> Success{Response<br/>Ready?}
    
    Success -->|Error| ErrorMsg[Apologize & Ask to Rephrase]
